OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784137703
OL,3,CKing approves the Channel Islands'
OL,4,Cfirst female Bailiff
OL,6,FJessica Roland has been approved by
OL,7,Fthe King as the next Bailiff of
OL,8,FGuernsey.
OL,10,FShe will be the first woman to hold
OL,11,Fthe senior States role in the Channel
OL,12,FIslands.
OL,14,FMs Roland is currently the Deputy
OL,15,FBailiff and will succeed Sir Richard
OL,16,FMcMahon once he retires at the end of
OL,17,FAugust after six years in the top job.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
