PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784137703
OL,3,CKing approves the Channel Islands'
OL,4,Cfirst female Bailiff
OL,6,FShe was born in Guernsey and attended
OL,7,FForest Primary School, as well as the
OL,8,FGrammar School for Girls, before
OL,9,Ffurther education in Wales, England
OL,10,Fand France.
OL,12,FMs Roland was admitted as a solicitor
OL,13,Fin the UK in 1997, returning to
OL,14,FGuernsey shortly afterwards and
OL,15,Fqualifying as an advocate.
OL,17,FShe went on to become a managing
OL,18,Fpartner at a local law firm, taking up
OL,19,Fthe position of Deputy Bailiff in May
OL,20,F2020.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784137703
OL,3,CKing approves the Channel Islands'
OL,4,Cfirst female Bailiff
OL,6,FIn an interview with ITV News, Ms
OL,7,FRoland says that her appointment as
OL,8,Fthe Bailiwick of Guernsey's Chief
OL,9,FJudge is "an extraordinary thing".
OL,11,FShe explains: "It's a story about
OL,12,Fsocial mobility in modern-day
OL,13,FGuernsey. I didn't come from the right
OL,14,Ffamily, I didn't go to the right
OL,15,Fschool.
OL,17,F"You just have to, in the end, back
OL,18,Fyourself and believe in yourself."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
