OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784137703
OL,3,CKing approves the Channel Islands'
OL,4,Cfirst female Bailiff
OL,6,FThe position of Bailiff has existed
OL,7,Ffor more than 700 years, having been
OL,8,Festablished in 1278.
OL,10,FIt is the most senior citizen-held
OL,11,Frole in the island and the holder also
OL,12,Facts as President of the Court of
OL,13,FAppeal.
OL,15,FMs Roland will represent Guernsey at
OL,16,Fhome and abroad, including welcoming
OL,17,Fmembers of the Royal Family and other
OL,18,Fdignitaries on their visits to the
OL,19,Fisland.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
